Boda-boda paranoia
The death of Ssebulime has stirred mixed emotions among those who use boda-boda, or motorcycle taxi, as a popular form of affordable transport.
At least five high profile murders involving military chiefs, members of parliament, religious leaders have occurred in the last three years all performed by hitmen riding on motorbikes.
This has put both boda-boda drivers and high-level officials on high alert.
