As a baker, you can imagine how difficult having those fears is when Im going to take something out of the oven, and suddenly something doesnt move the way I expect it to or something like that, and I instantly freeze up and freak out.
[] Tomorrow I will be thinking of all those who had it much worse than me, and hoping that the people who are still alive and lost so much more are doing okay.
